This is a plugin for Bukkit made to simulate hardcore mode on Bukkit server.
Solomondg and I are working on this, and so far, a very simple outline of a plugin has been created. I hope that it will work soon.

Well, to keep this short, I'll sign off. Thanks a bunch to the Bukkit community (including the wonderful tutorials on the wiki which have greatly helped my understanding of the API), and good luck understanding our code.

